	<h1 class="title">股市低迷，奢侈品的消费者不买账了？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Hiroko Tabuchi， Amie Tsang</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-09-06 10:57:24 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/14487/medium/14487.jpg?1441429698" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


